ugh not mandatory to be signed to a Modeling Agency in order to become a model, it is still the ultimate goal for many models- and with good reason. Modeling agencies (legit agencies, that is) are frequently able to procure well-paid, high-profile jobs for their talent roster.\r\n\r\nModeling Agency Directory – A list of Modeling Agencies, by state\r\nDo you have any suggestions for topics you would like to see? Any questions you have specifically that you would love a professional model’s advice on?? Let us know in the comments section! We LOVE to hear from you!\r\n\r\nOne more thing to note- if you enjoyed or benefitted from these articles (or know someone else who will), please like and share! We want ModelMentors to be the gift that keeps on giving ? Thank you!', 'Model mentors offers free modeling advice', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'modelmentors-offers-free-modeling-advice', '', '', '2017-07-16 05:11:59', '2017-07-16 05:11:59', '', 0, 'http://demo.themeegg.com/themes/enews/?p=50', 0, 'post', '', 0),
